item.title: Katy Perry - Rise (Official Video)
item.description:
Katy Perry - Rise (Official Video)

In Katy Perrys neuem Musikvideo zu „Rise" sieht man, dass man Berge überwinden kann, wenn man immer weiterkämpft und an sich glaubt. Dazu singt sie symbolisch: "You'll be surprised, I will still rise."

item.title: Jake Bugg - 'Gimme The Love' (live on triple j)
item.description:
Jake Bugg - 'Gimme The Love' (live on triple j)

Jake Bugg performs a live acoustic version of his track 'Gimme The Love' in triple j's Like A Version studio. Like A Version is a segment on Australian radio station triple j. Every Friday morning a musician or band comes into the studio to play one of their own songs and a cover of a song they love.
